%html
  %head
    %meta{"http-equiv" => "Content-Type", :content => "text/html; charset=utf-8"}
  %body
    %h1 dogtag  :::  Chiditarod registration bot
    %h4
      Good news!  Your team fundraising page has been successfully created!

    %p
      We are partnering with Classy.org this year to take advantage of their awesome fundraising platform.
      If you are new to Classy.org, you should see a "Claim Your Account" email from Classy in your inbox. Please open that
      email and follow the instructions to setup your Classy account.  If you were already a Classy
      user, simply go to
      %a{:href=>"http://classy.org"}
        http://classy.org
      and login.

    %p
      Once you have logged in, you should see 2 entries on your profile page:
      %ol

        %li
          %h3
            Team:
            = @team.name
          %p
            This is your Team fundraising profile.  There are many ways to
            %a{:href=>"https://www.classy.org/team/#{@team.classy_id}/dashboard/overview"}
              customize
            your team profile. You can (and probably should) invite them to
            %a{:href=>"https://www.classy.org/team/#{@team.classy_id}"}
              join your team
            and help fundraise! All they need to do is click that link and click Join Team.
            Your team page will calculate how much your team has raised in total.  Complete with your fellow teams for
            Most Epic Fundraiser and show the world via the leaderboard!
          %ul
            %li
              %a{:href=>"https://www.classy.org/team/#{@team.classy_id}"}
                Main Page
            %li
              %a{:href=>"https://www.classy.org/team/#{@team.classy_id}/dashboard/overview"}
                Customize

        %li
          %h3
            Fundraiser:
            = @team.name
          %p
            This is the fundraising page we created for your personal user account, and is associated with your team fundraiser (above).
            There are also many ways to
            %a{:href=> "https://www.classy.org/fundraiser/#{@team.classy_fundraiser_page_id}/dashboard/overview"}
              customize
            your fundraiser page to tell your story.  It's easy! After customizing your page, it is very easy to
            %a{:href=> "https://www.classy.org/fundraiser/#{@team.classy_fundraiser_page_id}"}
              share it!
          %ul
            %li
              %a{:href=> "https://www.classy.org/fundraiser/#{@team.classy_fundraiser_page_id}"}
                Main Page
            %li
              %a{:href=> "https://www.classy.org/fundraiser/#{@team.classy_fundraiser_page_id}/dashboard/overview"}
                Customize





    %p
      Please try claiming your Classy account and rock that fundraiser!  If you have issues, questions, or concerns,
      we are here to help.. please email us at
      %a{:href=>"mailto:fundraising@chiditarod.org"}
        fundraising@chiditarod.org

    %p
      xoxo,
      %br
      %a{:href=>"mailto:dogtag@chiditarod.org"}
        dogtag bot
